{"ID":"20260305082131-flcaji7","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-flcaji7","tags":"课程/CPP程序设计","title":"虚基类","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-5r7x0k1","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-5r7x0k1"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: 虚基类\ndate created: 星期三, 十月 22日 2025, 9:26:20 上午\ndate modified: 星期三, 十月 22日 2025, 2:42:53 下午\ntags:\n  - 课程/CPP程序设计\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bm82ai1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bm82ai1","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 虚基类的定义"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-jl12v92","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jl12v92","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关键字为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"virtual"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，把多个\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e逻辑对象\u003c/font\u003e映射成同一个\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e物理对象\u003c/font\u003e，共享同一个存储空间。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚基类尽可能早地构造、尽可能晚地析构，都只进行一次。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-tvhlys2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tvhlys2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"特性："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bdydv4v","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bdydv4v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-1m715pl","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1m715pl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-yvqb0lj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yvqb0lj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚基类与基类同名时，它们\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e分别拥有各自的存储空间\u003c/font\u003e，会导致二义性访问；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-mg2fw2a","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-mg2fw2a","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ujai6in","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ujai6in","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只有\u003cfont color=\"#c0504d\"\u003e同一棵派生树\u003c/font\u003e的\u003cfont color=\"#c0504d\"\u003e同名虚基类\u003c/font\u003e才共享存储空间，参考 [[多继承#^3e396a|声明对象作为成员时的派生树生成规则]]；"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vsm2q7y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vsm2q7y","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"建议："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 将基类说明为对象成员，或将基类都说明为虚基类。可用作用域运算符限定要访问的成员。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2082duh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2082duh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在虚继承中，\u003cfont color=\"#c0504d\"\u003e最派生类\u003c/font\u003e负责直接初始化虚基类。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fgq0s59","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fgq0s59","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"struct A { \n\tint a;\n\tA(int a) { this-\u003ea = a; cout \u003c\u003c \"a= \"\u003c\u003ca\u003c\u003cendl; }\n};\n\nstruct B :virtual public A { \n\tint b;\n\tB(int b):A(3) { // A(3) 并不会调用\n\t\tB::b = b; cout \u003c\u003c\"b = \"\u003c\u003cb\u003c\u003cendl; \n\t}\n};\n\nstruct C :virtual public A { \n\tint c;\n\tC(int c):A(5) { // A(5) 也并不会调用\n\t\tC::c = c; cout \u003c\u003c \" c = \"\u003c\u003cc\u003c\u003cendl; \n\t}\n};\n\nstruct D : public B, public C { \n\tint d;\n\tD(int b,int c,int d):C(c),B(b),A(111) { // 关键：负责直接初始化虚基类\n\t\tD::d = d; cout \u003c\u003c \" d = \"\u003c\u003cd\u003c\u003cendl; \n\t} \n};\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-q287ups","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-q287ups","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"该派生类的派生树如下："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"![[继承-5.png|350]]"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-zydoc2x","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zydoc2x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 派生类成员"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-prdrizy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-prdrizy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当派生类有多个基类或虚基类时，基类或虚基类的成员之间可能\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e出现同名\u003c/font\u003e；派生类和基类或虚基类的成员之间也可能出现同名。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-td0xq4u","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-td0xq4u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ffzt3w0","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ffzt3w0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-oxuksba","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-oxuksba","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"出现上述同名问题时，必须通过面向对象的作用域解析，或者用基类名加作用域运算符 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"::"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 指定要访问的成员，否则就会引起二义性问题。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-zv436kg","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zv436kg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-pjl9x31","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pjl9x31","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当派生类成员和基类成员同名时，\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e优先访问作用域小的成员\u003c/font\u003e，即优先访问派生类的成员。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-64zrdep","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-64zrdep","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-qflzhlf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qflzhlf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当派生类数据成员和派生类函数成员的参数同名时，在函数成员内优先访问函数参数。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-zdfdgv2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zdfdgv2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3 单重及多重继承的构造与析构"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-s16kjkg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-s16kjkg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"析构和构造的顺序相反，派生类对象的构造顺序："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-z1acfy6","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-z1acfy6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-8mgmgr4","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8mgmgr4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-afhoxn3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-afhoxn3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"按后根遍历的顺序，构造倒派生树中所有\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e虚基类\u003c/font\u003e；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-p6dbs57","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-p6dbs57","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-3m64ff9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3m64ff9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"按定义顺序构造派生类的所有\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e直接基类\u003c/font\u003e；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-wn245a5","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-wn245a5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-beoroex","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-beoroex","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"按定义顺序构造 (初始化) 派生类的\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e所有数据成员\u003c/font\u003e，包括对象成员、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 成员和引用成员；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4k5kuyx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4k5kuyx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-5jyrxtn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5jyrxtn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"执行派生类\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e自身的构造函数体\u003c/font\u003e。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果构造中虚基类、基类、对象成员、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 及引用成员又是派生类对象，则派生类对象重复上述构造过程（但同名虚基类对象在同一棵派生树中仅构造一次）。"}]}]}]}]}